metadata.description:
In celebration of my genesis drop, I am excited to share a new voice for ‘The Talking Palm Tree’, stripped down to her raw essence. 
Now… I L O V E making electronic music, but crafting this rendition reminded me how important it is to know a song in its simplest form… & it felt really, really good to get back & reconnect with my piano roots after all this time.

I offer this as a gift to all of you who collected the original song.

 <3 ♅
metadata.name: The Talking Palm Tree (Acoustic) #1
